#. type: YAML Front Matter: title
#. mt: gemini
#: _guides/security-openid-connect-client-registration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "OpenID Connect (OIDC) and OAuth2 dynamic client registration"
msgstr "Registro dinâmico de cliente OpenID Connect (OIDC) e OAuth2"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _guides/security-openid-connect-client-registration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "<a class=\"status-label status-experimental\" title=\"This extension requests early feedback to mature the idea\" href=\"#extension-status-note\">experimental</a>"
msgstr "<a class=\"status-label status-experimental\" title=\"Esta extensão solicita feedback inicial para amadurecer a ideia\" href=\"#extension-status-note\">experimental</a>"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _guides/security-openid-connect-client-registration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Typically, you have to register an OIDC client (application) manually in your OIDC provider's dashboard.\n"
"During this process, you specify the human readable application name, allowed redirect and post logout URLs, and other properties.\n"
"After the registration has been completed, you copy the generated client id and secret to your Quarkus OIDC application properties."
msgstr ""
"Normalmente, você precisa registrar um cliente OIDC (aplicação) manualmente no painel do seu provedor OIDC.\n"
"Durante esse processo, você especifica o nome legível da aplicação, as URLs de redirecionamento e pós-logout permitidas, e outras propriedades.\n"
"Após o registro ser concluído, você copia o ID do cliente e o segredo gerados para as propriedades da sua aplicação Quarkus OIDC."

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _guides/security-openid-connect-client-registration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"OpenID Connect and OAuth2 dynamic client registration allows you to register OIDC clients dynamically, and manage individual client registrations.\n"
"You can read more about it in the https://openid.net/specs/openid-connect-registration-1_0.html[OIDC client registration] and https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/html/rfc7592[OAuth2 Dynamic Client Registration Management Protocol] specification documents."
msgstr ""
"O registro dinâmico de cliente OpenID Connect e OAuth2 permite que você registre clientes OIDC dinamicamente e gerencie registros de clientes individuais.\n"
"Você pode ler mais sobre isso nos documentos de especificação https://openid.net/specs/openid-connect-registration-1_0.html[OIDC client registration] e https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/html/rfc7592[OAuth2 Dynamic Client Registration Management Protocol]."

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _guides/security-openid-connect-client-registration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "You can use Quarkus `quarkus-oidc-client-registration` extension to register one or more clients using OIDC client registration configurations and read, update and delete metadata of the registered clients."
msgstr "Você pode usar a extensão Quarkus `quarkus-oidc-client-registration` para registrar um ou mais clientes usando configurações de registro de cliente OIDC e ler, atualizar e excluir metadados dos clientes registrados."

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _guides/security-openid-connect-client-registration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "xref:security-openid-connect-multitenancy.adoc#tenant-config-resolver[OIDC TenantConfigResolver] can be used to create OIDC tenant configurations using the metadata of the registered clients."
msgstr "O xref:security-openid-connect-multitenancy.adoc#tenant-config-resolver[OIDC TenantConfigResolver] pode ser usado para criar configurações de tenant OIDC usando os metadados dos clientes registrados."

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _guides/security-openid-connect-client-registration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Currently, Quarkus `quarkus-oidc-client-registration` extension has an `experimental` status.\n"
"Dynamic client registration API provided by this extension may change while this extension has an experiemental status."
msgstr ""
"Atualmente, a extensão Quarkus `quarkus-oidc-client-registration` tem status `experimental`.\n"
"A API de registro dinâmico de cliente fornecida por esta extensão pode mudar enquanto ela tiver o status experimental."

#. type: Title =
#. mt: gemini
#: _guides/security-openid-connect-client-registration.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "OIDC Client Registration"
msgstr "Registro de Cliente OIDC"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
